 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6235367a-7fbe-4683-94ff-cd8fca9a54cb\" style=\"color:#36851e;\">□ 납품 및 구매확정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a0b317b-206e-4065-84c6-3c3585f9cc67\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-791bd815-077e-4b9c-99fc-94c13c754f42\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-41f55792-f133-495b-87d6-cfd14c1624f7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2164a99f-2de8-46a1-a436-1a600e4f0a07\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22401771-1d9e-478f-a2fa-b5d017c2d751\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0f12066e-69db-418a-b73f-83e0fd3ee1b7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 자신의 인쇄물을 궁금해하시는 고객님을 위해 최선을 다해 사진이나 동영상 등으로 바로바로 전달드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a45b5229-e6e6-4971-8125-ea1de5fe6f7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c25f4854-c810-4103-9bcd-6fc741c38ab2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a445431-42fa-415c-a38a-c25adfdf19ed\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-864d7e6a-f747-4881-ae36-018bef23dacc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eb8e175a-05f9-4978-a619-1ea5a1633777\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c56c11b7-80c9-437b-8ee5-10ff9a182556\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f05af767-8063-47bd-b049-2efab71f632b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e0d07dbc-e3d1-43ef-a19b-367a00f11082\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 저희도 리스크는 존재합니다. 모든 인쇄물을 전달해 드리기는 어렵고 모든 고객님에게 시간과 스케줄상 함께 하지는 못한다는 점 미리 양해의 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-864f7640-18f7-4d7f-a075-4a9877ca6df4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e06fb68f-c555-4d23-807d-214ee15e425a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07b4466c-78a9-4487-8273-8f6290c0e402\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-432af80f-05af-4c65-bc85-58b05e0f4c50\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>발주 사양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e6bf34ce-6690-43a1-844c-6fba0ebd45b2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a5bd692-2ce8-44f7-bd6d-3d6f48df69d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35b2e429-2770-4bdf-8046-0e3b12bdef2e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8d4b81d-4131-4352-8d68-94590b49771f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-686096ff-96f2-4f7c-8e6c-f0d9562f426d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c7d86134-cf60-44a3-8101-46e3768256d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>소량 200개를 2단 싸바리</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f115a71c-40aa-4b83-a6a6-6ac117024156\" style=\"color:#555555;\">로 만들었습니다. 거의 대부분의 업체가 제작해 주지 않는 수량과 형태입니다. 하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 납기와 단가를 최고의 노하우로 제작하여 제공해 드리고 있습니다. 언제든 궁금한 사항은 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-d3717aae-10c4-4a24-ae0d-cb79fc7f3f25\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b3d9b3e-d200-4c59-b160-73576d181276\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2744502a-ed3d-4c31-bb22-2d4aaa24f248\" style=\"\">제작 시 주의 사항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce721ac7-51fb-4b91-9769-613f0939530b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-85a7cbc1-06ec-4fb0-8033-f457154be969\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-127189a0-324e-4c82-b9a4-456372bbc836\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>색상 감리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f1015a49-1870-4497-89bf-268b20d9c0f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6baf88a7-cec5-47db-be3d-da9d89d34d7e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63d83037-0112-4750-881d-b4a0b0c77e69\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-68f02d15-12d6-4dac-9d5b-9ad7b462d3ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\">CMYK 인쇄 시에 내외부의 색상을 맞춰서 작업하는 건 중요합니다. 박스 색상을 외부와 내부의 색상으로 통일하여 진행했을 때 동일하게 맞추는 건 정말 어렵습니다. 특히 소량의 경우는 더더욱 어렵습니다. 이럴 때 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-88241303-7fe3-4c64-9913-355d60e13d3d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>별색을 사용</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c26a2aa-b348-4b76-8ecb-ec835c67f71d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하기도 합니다. 별색으로 진행하면 약간은 색상을 통일감 있게 맞추기 쉽습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7fe2c495-33b3-40cd-af55-01e91c63884b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-61f571cb-f34a-494a-ac95-b447f970fc88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f5e77d7-a35a-4732-bc5f-57dea6640fb6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-48a742f9-b9bd-47ac-952f-ccf63260ac22\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4bed775-0073-41d6-a5aa-9946bb269516\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-33932fb9-d79b-439d-936a-f830824242b0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>내부 패드 작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f9af2d6-9719-44f1-a47b-2fbc09df5831\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d79ab92e-e241-45e3-991e-09e143447aee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a48bc163-57cf-418d-baea-dcc4189f8e88\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9db84a5a-646e-4eb5-8ebf-8d103bb2e7f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸바리 박스에서 내부 패드 작업이 가장 사고나 문제가 발생될 확률이 높습니다. 제품에 안 맞거나 인쇄 등등의 견적이 달라지는 현상 등으로 트러블이 종종 생깁니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 그러한 문제를 해결하기 위해 계약 전에 반드시 상담을 통해 정확한 가 견적을 드리려고 노력 중입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43e01f8b-a655-4764-b243-ebf61fca78d0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5a560071-49c4-40aa-979f-4ea1fe7828f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b297059e-0b82-4868-b1f7-2225dbc5aed8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db8cc0ef-cb08-41e4-949a-4ae6bf803673\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 그렇게 진행한다고 하더라도 고객님의 상황이나 여건의 변화로 인해 추가 견적이 발생하거나 제품의 사양 자체가 달라질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16a4e1e6-08ce-4358-9f54-207e44d144dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e0522fb-44a6-4c05-8437-66368df7e850\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-237a9e7d-d336-4c5b-935d-90b00973d4ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d3fd7ace-797e-49b1-9438-838718d036ba\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니은 약간은 융통성은 발휘</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4efb9ca4-0577-40e2-8044-c0636e3d5eb8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하여 제작해 드리고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b9f0a62-7df6-4c9f-86c2-8a1cfeb5fad8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3301f39-afee-40dd-b1dd-4cd44587adb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-650d6329-ffdb-4e41-878b-2afa4a0a8d8d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1d3e645d-4315-401f-914f-41df0c9f9c6c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이번 작업도 하짝과 내부 패드의 인쇄는 없고 흰 싸바리 색상으로 진행되는 것으로 먼저 이야기되었었습니다. 하지만 추후 여러 문제가 발생될 소지가 있어 약간의 비용 추가로 수정해 드렸습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b9d5ff5b-6de3-4aff-bfc8-7779675432b0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5fa45f1f-07bf-4f6c-a3bf-1d65a75bff1d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224026129938/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-737e151b-94d8-488e-9a2d-97793944bebe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2f24e9ee-2fc2-4d28-ae44-8c4bf90196b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-79572209-d699-4acd-b15b-184f8bfe89e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6b75325b-6f30-4386-a3b9-501e87f81e7b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-626f76b8-90c6-423a-a30e-4a2c41e86719\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e868f1a3-c072-4ef2-a13d-e9b463ab808f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4c4ed5c7-cba8-47b7-80c9-341c05457ae3\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>배송 및 마무리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-681bdc8f-7c9a-4dfc-a54c-0223841f64c7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31da83c4-6cb2-4d61-a85c-25f160df5121\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c93e76b-9f50-41b4-b3b9-f21baac25d2d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-466033d0-e0a9-4821-93b3-969a620f07cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">싸바리작업의 완료는 배송입니다. 부피가 크다 보니 배송이나 적재에 큰 비용이나 노력이 들어갑니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aadc0704-bf10-458b-96af-c863138995a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9175b79d-46a2-4dcb-96cc-3b30000a253d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">항상 배송에 최적인 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de2